OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,FIrish actress Jessie Buckley has
OL,7,Fspoken about her struggle with her
OL,8,Fmental health as a teenager, and has
OL,9,Fcredited her love of music and theatre
OL,10,Ffor helping with her recovery.
OL,12,FBuckley, 36, from Killarney, Co Kerry,
OL,13,Fhas been a juggernaut through awards
OL,14,Fseason, receiving a string of awards
OL,15,Ffor her performance as William
OL,16,FShakespeare's wife Agnes Hathaway,
OL,17,Fhistorically known as Anne, in the
OL,18,Fadaptation of Maggie O'Farrell's novel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
