PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,FBuckley described acting as
OL,7,F"essential" and said it is "like water
OL,8,Fto me", adding that her passion for
OL,9,Fher craft helped her to overcome an
OL,10,Feating disorder and depression during
OL,11,Fher school years.
OL,13,FSpeaking on Radio 4's Desert Island
OL,14,FDiscs with Lauren Laverne, Buckley
OL,15,Fsaid: "I didn't know how to be alive
OL,16,Fthe way I wanted to be, and it was
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]oD@\OUpD@FO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,F"But I do not for a second regret it,
OL,7,Fand I think I've been able to
OL,8,Ftransform it and recognise our
OL,9,Fvulnerabilities as humans in the world.
OL,11,F"You can't walk through life not being
OL,12,Faffected, but you can transform that
OL,13,Finto something that allows you to be
OL,14,Fmore human and alive in the way that
OL,15,Fyou want to be."
OL,17,FShe continued: "When I moved to
OL,18,FLondon, I still wasn't out of the
OL,19,Fwoods.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@PO]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,F"I think there were moments where I
OL,7,Fwas like, 'if I don't get better here,
OL,8,Fthis music, this being part of theatre
OL,9,F` I'm not going to be able to do this
OL,10,Fany more, and I probably won't
OL,11,Fsurvive'.
OL,13,F"And that was the thing that turned it
OL,14,Fin my head, I was like, 'I don't want
OL,15,Fto sacrifice that, this is bigger than
OL,16,Fthat', and won."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
