PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,FThe actress, who has been nominated
OL,7,Ffor an Oscar, remembered the first
OL,8,Ftime she performed on stage and said:
OL,9,F"It was like drinking water, you know?
OL,10,FI just think, the more I did it, the
OL,11,Fmore I realised this is essential to
OL,12,Fme."
OL,14,FBuckley also recounted her time on BBC
OL,15,Ftalent show I'd Do Anything, which was
OL,16,Fabout the search for an actress to
OL,17,Fplay Nancy in a West End production of
OL,18,FOliver!, and which catapulted her to
OL,19,Ffame.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
