OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,FIn an interview with British Vogue in
OL,7,FJanuary, she spoke about being
OL,8,Fcriticised for her appearance during
OL,9,Fher time on the show.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Laverne, Buckley said: "I
OL,12,Fdon't like that part of it.
OL,14,F"I think that was a young woman who's
OL,15,Ftrying to discover her body and
OL,16,Fherself, like we all do. And I wish
OL,17,Fthat hadn't happened.
OL,26,@sD@dOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,F"I think I was putting a brave face
OL,7,Fon, because really what I wanted to do
OL,8,Fwas sing and I wanted to act, and I
OL,9,Fwanted to be part of this industry,
OL,10,Fand all of a sudden you had to be a
OL,11,Fcertain kind of person.
OL,13,F"And I just wasn't, I never will be.
OL,14,FThat's just not me."
OL,16,FBuckley added: "I'm so proud of that
OL,17,Fgirl. I think she did great and I
OL,18,Fdon't regret any of it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@TO]xD@POUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
