CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772931778
OL,3,CJessie Buckley says passion for music
OL,4,Cand theatre helped her mental health
OL,6,FShe also spoke about her
OL,7,F"extraordinary" mother, and said: "My
OL,8,Fparents are no longer together, and
OL,9,Fshe lives in Dublin, and she's writing
OL,10,Fher own story right now at 60 years of
OL,11,Fage, and I'm so proud of her."
OL,13,FShe sounded emotional as she gave her
OL,14,Ffirst song choice, which was a
OL,15,Frendition of her mother, Marina,
OL,16,Fsinging O Holy Night in church.
OL,18,FListen to the full Desert Island Disc
OL,19,Fepisode on BBC Sounds and BBC Radio 4
OL,20,Ffrom Sunday at 10am.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]oD@cOUsD@^O]
